{"tid":721540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到個post話d啊公啊婆係街推車仔 諗番起...","createTime":"2018-06-28T18:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T05:55:48.000Z","uid":148252,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ffaf15352eaa01e54b150bc26105a3e8ed0ef987","tid":721540,"uid":148252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"交代下背景先<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說小弟20出頭<br />\n有次係新蒲崗同女朋友食完飯 等過紅綠燈<br />\n前面有對中年夫婦 突然有個推車婆婆推住成車紙皮等過馬路 唔知婆婆係咪成日未食飯 係到問人可唔可以俾幾十蚊佢買飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢兩個即刻彈開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後過完馬路 我拉住女朋友放慢腳步 見到個婆婆一路行一路問 但都冇人幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最後我衝左入去燒味鋪叫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：一個叉雞飯加罐可樂 拎走<br />\n再狗衝過去俾婆婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：婆婆請你食吖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：多謝你啊😭<br />\n我留低一句<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔洗客氣 你慢慢食<br />\n然後就離開了<br />\n雖然唔知婆婆堅定流 但係好唔撚明d中年點解唔肯幫下人 鬼唔望佢有朝一日都變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係好多錢 利申 個飯30幾蚊 糧尾戶口得番100都冇 好似係. 幫到人就覺得無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c43c182f50832ded509ff19ee52d50c36d38234","tid":721540,"uid":170044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T18:11:29.000Z","msg":"哦 好撚有心"},{"pid":"0d5c3eff6b47bfee82773e26e8aeb0081f0dd3d7","tid":721540,"uid":148252,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"4c43c182f50832ded509ff19ee52d50c36d38234","tid":721540,"uid":170044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"ci